programme.title: Drama On 2 Waris Ep10
programme.desc: Ari tinggal bersama Mak Longnya di Ampang Batu setelah kejadian yang berlaku di Mendekar. Dia mendapat sokongan kakaknya, Kasma juga Tina, kawan baiknya. Begitu pun kehadirannya di situ tidak disenangi sebahagian penduduk kampung terutamanya Rubiah. Namun segalanya tidak mematahkan semangat Ari untuk terus berbakti mengubati penyakit dan membuat ubat-ubatan herba membantu mereka yang memerlukan bantuannya untuk berubat. Pada masa sama dia terpaksa berdepan dilema semangat harimau yang diwarisinya.

programme.title: Drama Cina Taste Of Happiness
programme.desc: Uncle Sui berdepan dengan persaingan daripada restoran-restoran moden di sekelilingnya. Pada masa sama, beliau perlu memikirkan kehidupan anak-anak perempuannya, Dao Xuan dan Mai Xian. Dao Xuan, seorang yang degil dan tegas terhadap orang sekelilingnya manakala Mai Xian, suri rumah yang lembut dan sangat mempercayai suaminya. Bagaimanapun, apabila anak-anaknya menghadapi masalah dalam perhubungan mereka, Uncle Sui merasakan inilah masa yang terbaik untuk dia mencurahkan kasih sayang terhadap mereka melalui makanan.

programme.title: Umar Hatta Ep7
programme.desc: Dahlia tak habis-habis menyucuk ibunya dengan menuduh Leyla gadis murahan yang tidak layak dibawa masuk ke dalam keluarga mereka. Puan Sri sedar Dahlia hanya berkata begitu kerana masih terluka dengan penolakan Hatta ke atasnya. Lalu Puan Sri memujuk Dahlia agar meredhakan jodoh Hatta. Puan Sri berjanji akan sama-sama mencarikan jodoh yang baik untuk Dahlia pula. Kepulangan Zafran yang tiba secara mengejut membuatkan Dahlia kembali gembira. Namun kegembiraan itu tergugat dengan kemarahan Zafran yang meledak secara tiba-tiba sebaik mendengar Hatta telah bertunang tanpa memberitahunya.

programme.title: Bintang Hatiku S2 Ep12

Goyang badan papanya namun tidak bergerak. Rahul makin kuat kejut papanya. Raziq tak bergerak jugak. Rahul susah hati dan kejutkan lagi namun tidak bangun juga lalu dia menjerit memanggil nendanya.

programme.desc: Natasya hanya berkelulusan SPM tetapi bijak, agak lasak dan adakala lebih bersifat seperti lelaki. Namun sesekali dia berdandan dan bersolek, pastinya kebanyakan pemuda kampung akan terpikat dengan kecantikan yang dimiliki oleh Natasya dan memanggilnya Puteri Gunung Ledang. Natasya berimpian menjadi model terkenal. Setiap kali mencuba nasib, dia gagal dan akhirnya bekerja sebagai kerani di sebuah agensi peragaan sahaja. Nasibnya berubah apabila dia menjadi duta produk kecantikan secara tidak sengaja. Ramai yang mula jatuh hati dan terpikat pada kecantikan Natasya termasuklah majikannya Rayyan. Bandi jatuh hati pada pandangan pertama dengan Riri, merasakan semangat yang baru untuk kesembuhannya. Sementara kakaknya, Haris, justru cemas kehadiran Riri akan memberi harapan palsu untuk Bandi.

programme.title: Dia Menantu Rahsia Ep04
programme.desc: Memaparkan kebetulan Zamer yang mengasari Melissa di kawasan blok tempat tinggalnya dilihat dan dibantu oleh Syakir. Melissa disyorkan berada di rumah dan bersama sepupunya. Ketika di rumah sepupu Melissa yang menghubungi ke kampung dapat pengesahan yang Zamer memang putus tunang. lantaran itu sepupu Melissa berharap Melissa tetapkan hati yakni jangan lagi berbalik kepadanya. Melissa akui dia semakin dapat melakukannya. Lain pula di pihak Zamir dia kelihatan bertekad untuk mendapatkan Melissa. Zamir yang memberitahu ibunya di kampung hingga terasa ibunya dia yang bersalah. Melissa mengalami trauma dan dia takut untuk bersendirian. Zulaikha sentiasa menemani Melissa. Kadang-kala Zulaikha menghantar dan mengambil Melissa di tempat kerja. Pada masa yang sama, Syakir juga risaukan keselamatan Melissa. Sepanjang hidupnya, dia tidak pernah melihat perempuan diserang sebegitu. Melissa yang bekerja semula kerap didatangi Syakir. Pernah Zamir cuba mendesak Melissa di tempat kerja. Akhirnya telah menceritakan segalanya pada Syakir siapakah lelaki yang menyerangnya itu. Lelaki itu adalah Zamir. Sementara Suhaimi dan dua anak-anaknya dalam hubungan yang baik, malah projek kerja mereka yang Suhaimi amanahkan kepada Syakir juga berjaya. ibu Syakir sering meminta Syakir memberi ruang masa kepada Engku Kemelia. Suatu hari ibu Syakir menggesa Syakir untuk pulang ke rumah. Syakir banyak kerja. Suatu hari ibunya membawa Engku Kamelia ke pejabat pun tidak dilayan Syakir. Engku Razzi pernah bersemuka dengan Syakir dan dia berterus terang pintunya telah tertutup untuk Engku Kamelia. Sedang Engku Kamelia merasai dia seperti tiada wujud. Sarah, ibu Syakir terus berbaik dan memujuk Engku kamelia dan secara mengejut mereka ke pejabat Syakir lagi. Mereka keluar bertiga dan kemudiannya Sarah, ibunya pulang dahulu. Syakir berterus terang dia tidak boleh menerima Engku Kamelia kerana dia akan teringat apa yang dilakukan oleh Engku Kamela dahulu. Pintunya telah tertutup. Syakir tanpa diketahui ahli keluarganya terutama abangnya sendiri kerap menemui Melissa. Dengan keadaan Melissa, Syakir akhirnya dengan serius dan ikhlas mengajak Melissa menjadi teman hidupnya. Melissa terpinga-pinga seolah berada dalam mimpi dan masih tidak berkata apa-apa.

programme.title: Momzillas
programme.desc: Dua wanita terlibat dalam konflik langsung apabila anak-anak mereka mengumumkan hasrat mereka untuk berkahwin. Walau bagaimanapun, mereka perlu mengetepikan perbezaan mereka apabila mereka berdua terdampar di pulau yang jauh.

programme.title: Secebis Rindu Ep02
programme.desc: Reeza pandai bermain dengan situasi hingga membuatkan Rasya selesa dengan Reeza. Rasya mula dibuai oleh perasaan atas layanan baik & mesra oleh Reeza. Reeza mahu berjumpa dengan Rasya dan jawapan Rasya pantas menjawab TIDAK. Opah beritahu Rasya yang dia nak jodohkan Rasya dengan Fahmi. Rasya terkejut sebab Rasya belum bersedia dan tak pernah cintakan Fahmi.

programme.title: Sembang Selebriti S7 Ep01
programme.desc: Sembang selebriti merupakan rancangan bual bicara bersama selebriti yang menceritakan tentang pengalaman mereka di dalam dunia seni tanahair yang boleh dijadikan sumber inspirasi.

programme.title: Mr Wrong Ep36
programme.desc: Ezgi dan zgr, yang kali terakhir bergaduh dan membatalkan perjanjian itu, terkejut apabila mereka mengetahui bahawa mereka akan bekerjasama. Ozan, yang menyaksikan detik-detik ini, tidak tahu apa yang perlu dilakukan. Adalah sangat penting bagi Ozan untuk bekerjasama dengan Ezgi, walaupun dia bercakap dengan zgr dan cuba membetulkan keadaan ia tidak berjaya. Sementara itu, kejutan kedua menanti Ezgi. Dalam menghadapi kejadian ini, Ezgi menyoal dirinya sendiri dan menganggap dia bertindak salah dengan zgr. Dia mahu membetulkan hubungannya dengan zgr. Keinginan Ezgi untuk datang ke majlis perkahwinan membuatkan zgr gembira. Kedua-duanya bersedia untuk bermain permainan, tidak menyedari apa yang akan berlaku kepada mereka.

programme.title: Jodoh Sebelah Pintu S1 Ep05
programme.desc: Julia bergaduh kecil dengan Mimi dan Mona selepas Irfan dan Badrul menggunakan mereka sebagai alasan untuk reject Julia. Mona bertambah marah pada jiran lelakinya itu lalu mencari jalan untuk terus mengenakan mereka. Selepas kedatangan jiran baru, Taufik dan Amirul, Julia mula ada sasaran baru. Mona menerima SMS dan panggilan misteri tetapi tidak melayannya. Akhirnya, diketahui bahawa panggilan itu datangnya daripada bakal tunangnya, Alang. Mona memberanikan diri untuk mula berhubung dengan Alang. Badrul cuba mengacau Irfan dengan prank surat cinta misteri di tempat kerja. Masalah lebih besar berlaku apabila surat itu jatuh ke tangan Dr. Norma, doktor yang terkenal dengan ketegasannya.

programme.title: The Trial
programme.desc: Ronald, seorang pelajar cacat mental, dituduh merogol Bessy, tutor dan guru sekolahnya. Tetapi sebagai pelajar darjah tujuh berusia 29 tahun, Ronald adalah "kes khas" dalam lebih daripada satu cara.

Kedua dua kumpulan perlu menari sepadan dengan rentak lagu yang dimainkan. Markah akan diambil kira daripada kekuatan jeritan para penonton. Pertandingan untuk memenangi RM6,000 sememangnya susah kerana peserta juga perlu bersaing di dalam 2 mini games. Markah tertinggi di penghujung rancangan akan menjadi juara untuk episod ini. Kumpulan lelaki yang mengumpul lebih markah telah diistihar sebagai pemenang.

programme.title: Saat Hati Telah Memilih Ep03
programme.desc: Mengangkat kisah cinta segitiga antara Riri (Aurelia), Bandi (Ricky Harun), dan Haris (Ali Syakieb). Riri seorang mahasiswi kedokteran yang merasa jenuh dengan hidupnya yang penuh aturan, bertemu dengan Bandi yang menderita penyakit jantung kronis. Bandi jatuh hati pada pandangan pertama dengan Riri, merasakan semangat yang baru untuk kesembuhannya. Sementara kakaknya, Haris, justru cemas kehadiran Riri akan memberi harapan palsu untuk Bandi.

programme.title: Resepi Moyang S5 Ep03

programme.title: Dapur Bujang S6 Ep16
programme.desc: Dengan bajet RM10, Naem tukang masak Dapur Bujang akan menyediakan dua jenis hidangan masakan harian yang senang, sedap dan sihat. Untuk episod ini, Naem akan memasak Ayam Goreng Halia dan Zalabia sejenis cucur yang manis yang berasal dari timur tenggah.

programme.title: Rock 4: Rockers Never Dai
programme.desc: Filem ini mengisahkan liku-liku kehidupan yang dilalui oleh bekas ahli kumpulan muzik rock terkenal di era 90an, Rimba Bara. Namun kerana gejala dadah, masalah peribadi yang tidak terkawal dan kemalangan ngeri yang menimpa, kehidupan anggota kumpulan musnah. Seorang yang koma kembali sedar, membawa sinar baru apabila dia berjaya menguruskan kumpulan muzik rock baru menggunakan nama kumpulan lama; Rimba Bara II diterajui oleh pemuda yang juga jirannya. Pelbagai cabaran dan halangan ditempuhi sebelum kumpulan mereka berjaya dan menempa nama dalam industri muzik rock tanah air. Di akhir penceritaan dibekal dengan semangat kental dan sentiasa positif dalam hidup, pengurus dan semua ahli kumpulan pemuzik rock berjaya dan mencapai cita masing-masing sekali gus kehidupan yang bahagia.

programme.title: Poskad Dari Alhambra Ep05
programme.desc: Mr Johnson balik ke KL bincang dengan Headmaster Mr Daniel untuk buat pertandingan persahabatan dengan pelajar pondok Tok Guru Nik Ahmad. Mereka kata simboliknya nak tunjukkan bangsa dan empayar British mereka masih gagah dan berkuasa. Daniel setuju kerana ia boleh jadi bahan latihan sebelum bertanding dan berlawan dengan team Penang Free School,English College dan MCKK.

programme.title: Talk Back And You're Dead
programme.desc: Ini adalah kisah Samantha, seorang gadis yang jatuh cinta secara luar biasa dengan seorang lelaki yang delinkuen, panas kepala bernama Top--ketua geng yang dipanggil "Lucky 13". Dan dia selalu bertanya pada dirinya sama ada ia akan kekal selama-lamanya.

programme.title: Rojak S5 Ep13
programme.desc: Rojak adalah sebuah rancangan yang membawa pelbagai jenis informasi yang mendedahkan orang awan kepada benda yang mereka tidak biasanya akan cuba dari experiment sosial, D.I.Y, dan juga makanan yang tidak biasa jumpe.

programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep26
programme.desc: Memaparkan Nizam (Angah) dan Mizan (Along) dua beradik dari satu keluarga. Nizam lulusan luar negeri, bekerjaya, baru berkahwin dan baru juga bercerai. Hubungan Nizam dan Mizan tidak mesra sangat. ibu bapa mereka juga memelihara Hani, sebagai adik angkat. Kini, Hani seorang gadis, selain sangat disayangi ibu bapa mereka, Mizan pula mencintainya. Jalinan percintaan mereka juga direstui ibu bapa mereka, cuma Nizam terpaksa menangguhkan perkahwinan mereka sekurang-kurangnya 3 tahun kerana melanjutkan pelajaran keluar negara. Hani yang baik sahsiahnya dan berbudi pekerti, pandai mengemas rumah tangga memahaminya dan sanggup menunggu. Di hari ketibaan Nizam pulang, ibu bapanya telah menetapkan sebagai hari perkahwinan Nizam dan Hani. Selain majlis telah siap, tetamu juga telah dijemput, tiba-tiba sehari sebelum majlis berlangsung, Nizam meminta majlis dibatalkan dengan alasan dia telah berkahwin 5 bulan lalu. Di hari itu, Mizan juga pulang sebagai meraikan majlis adiknya, lalu ibu bapanya mencadangkan Mizan menggantikan tempat Nizam. Mizan agak terkejut dan tidak bersetuju walau pun dirayu demi menutup maruah keluarga. Sementara itu Hani amat berduka, tetapi sebelah malamnya Hani berubah hati semata-mata demi maruah keluarga lalu merayu beberapa kali kepada Mizan mengambilnya sebagai isteri. Mizan bukan sahaja menolak permintaan Hani, sebaliknya mencerca Hani yang dianggap tidak malu. Hani pula terus berdoa. Di awal pagi hari majlis, Mizan berubah hati dan bersetuju. Majlis perkahwinan Mizan dan Hani serta jamuan berjalan lancar. Di sebelah petangnya. Nizam dan isterinya, Shela juga tiba dan mereka dijangka akan tinggal di situ beberapa ketika.

programme.title: Dia Menantu Rahsia Ep05
programme.desc: Memaparkan Melissa dari kampung telah menumpang tinggal di rumah sepupunya Zulaikha di bandar kerana dia ditawarkan bekerja di sebuah cafe iaitu "Book Cafe". Sekali gus dia merasai lega setelah kekecewaan dengan kekasihnya, Zamer yang terpaksa mengikut kehendak pilihan ibunya. Zamer masih teringatkan Melissa dan merasai Dr Suraya, pilihan ibunya tidak sesuai. Secara kebetulan Syakir tinggal di blok Melissa dan sepupunya tinggal cuma di tingkat lain. Syakir tidak tahu setakat ini Melissa bekerja di "Book Cafe" milik anak syarikat bapanya. Syakir menyelia tempat itu tetapi hanya datang beberapa hari sahaja dalam sebulan. Pun begitu Syakir secara diam-diam memerhati dan minat terhadap Melissa terutamanya ketika balik kerja, gelagat Melissa menyayangi anak kucing (panggilan baby). Melissa tidak perasan. Sebelum itu sepupu Melissa yang mendapati tayer keretanya pancit di halaman blok, Zulaikha dan Melissa meminta Syakir membantu, tetapi Syakir berlalu sahaja. Cuma dalam diam-diam dia menelefon mekanik yang dia tahu. Syakir anak usahawan pasangan Suhaimi dan Sarah. Syakir dua beradik dan adik kepada Shamsul. Hubungan Shamsul dengan adiknya baik, begitu juga Syakir dan Shamsul dengan bapa mereka. Shamsul telah berkahwin dengan Nora. Shamsul dan isterinya tidak tinggal bersekali dengan ibu dan bapa mereka. Syakir tinggal berasingan. Sifat ibunya sentiasa mendesak Syakir berkahwin tetapi hanya dengan pilihannya. Akibat itu Syakir kadang kala tidak berminat berbual hal berkahwin. Malah dia pernah bertunang dengan Engku Kamela, anak Engku Maimunah tetapi diputuskan Syakir. Hanya Syakir sahaja yang tahu sebabnya membuatkan adik lelaki Engku Kamela tidaklah bermusuhan tetapi berharap Syakir nyatakan sebabnya. Terkini, ibu Syakir datang ke pejabat dan dia ingin menjodohkan Syakir dengan Engku Kamelia, kembar seiras bekas tunangnya, Selama ini Engku Kamelia tinggal di luar negara sejak kecil. Ini membuatkan Syakir kurang senang dan tidak menyukainya, selain merasai tidak patut dia berbuat demikian.

programme.desc: Mengisahkan Rachel yang di bunuh dengan kejam oleh David dan kawan-kawannya. Rachel di bunuh demi menutupi salah guna kuasa David di dalam syarikat. Roh Rachel yang tidak tenteram merayau mencari pembunuhnya sehingga dia bertemu dengan ke empat-empat Lelaki tersebut.

programme.title: 4 Tahun Tinggal Di Rumah Hantu
programme.desc: 4 Tahun Tinggal di Rumah Hantu adalah film horor Indonesia yang dirilis pada tahun 2014. Film ini merupakan adaptasi sebuah novel berdasarkan kisah nyata yang menceritakan rumah hantu di Kota Depok, Jawa Barat

programme.title: Taxi 5
programme.desc: Seorang pegawai polis yang ditukarkan dalam polis Marseilles ditugaskan untuk menumpaskan sekumpulan perompak Itali yang memandu Ferrari berkuasa bersama anak saudara Daniel yang lebih tua, seorang pemandu yang teruk yang mendapat teksi putih legenda.

programme.title: Dendam Sarakit S1 Ep3
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Mariam berjumpa Tok Moh yang mengatakan dia telah diganggu penjelmaan seorang wanita dan tidak lagi mahu berterusan dengan tugasan memisahkan Rafiq dan Sarakit. Mengimbas balik, Mariam enggan memberikan kebenaran untuk Rafiq berkahwin dengan Sarakit. Mariam telah berjumpa Tok Moh untuk memisahkan Rafiq dari Sarakit yang menyebabkan Sarakit diganggu mimpi ngeri. Kini, Mariam pula diganggu penjelmaan Sarakit dan perkara ini diceritakan kepada Rafiq. Rafiq mengambil keputusan untuk pulang kerana memikirkan Sarakit yang masih belum dapat dihubungi. Ramdi pula diganggu hantu tenggek yang dibawa merayau-rayau setiap malam. Pada satu malam, Pak Bado pula mendengar suara bayi menangis dan mendapati bungkusan mengandungi janin di hadapan rumahnya yang diletak oleh lembaga putih berambut panjang.

Dia berusaha untuk menolong gadis itu sesuaikan diri dengan gaya hidup bandar dan akhirnya gadis kampung itu juga telah jatuh cinta kepadanya. Walaubagaimanapun kerana sifatnya yang matang, ramai wanita mencemburuinya.

programme.desc: Mengisahkan mayat Zai ditemui oleh orang kampung Paya Besar dengan kesan jerutan di leher pada esok paginya. Mayat Zai diuruskan oleh keluarganya. Salah seorang yang hadir adalah sepupu Zai, Sulaiman. Sulaiman terkejut bila melihat kesan kematian Zai seperti pernah dilihatnya 50 tahun dulu iaitu kematian Awang. programme.desc: Daniel dan Cynthia, pasangan muda dengan anak dalam perjalanan, mengalami masa sukar di Manila. Mereka kembali ke Baguio, tempat asal Daniel, untuk memulakan semula. Melalui kebaikan Alex, kawan Daniel zaman kanak-kanak yang kaya, mereka dapat tinggal di sebuah rumah besar, tanpa sewa; dan dia mendapat tawaran kerja juga. Segala-galanya seolah-olah jatuh pada tempatnya untuk mereka - atau begitulah yang mereka fikirkan - sehingga perkara aneh mula berlaku di rumah mereka.

programme.title: Diva Popular
programme.desc: Mengisahkan pertembungan di antara pelakon senior, Erna Teteyye dengan pelakon baharu, Tasha. Erna ialah seorang pelakon popular yang telah lama berkecimpung dalam perniagaan pertunjukan di Malaysia, dan telah memenangi pelbagai anugerah untuk persembahannya. Pada suatu hari, teman lelakinya, Faizal diberi peluang untuk mengarahkan filem baharu terbitan Julie, namun keadaan menjadi kelam kabut apabila Julie memilih Tasha sebagai heroin filem itu. Pada malam Anugerah Artis Paling Popular Berita Harian, mereka berdua terpilih sebagai finalis untuk anugerah tersebut. Persoalannya, siapakah pemenang dalam pertarungan ini?

From touching sibling love, to the struggles and entanglement of parent-child relationship, the show elaborates on the importance of encountering the surroundings with a positive attitude. Through a bowl of beef noodle soup, Hui-wen and Chien-chin teach their four daughters, Spring, Summer, Fall, and Winter, how to behave around others. The heartwarming play is relaxing, fun, humorous, and a tearjerker.

programme.title: Blessing of Formosa(T) Ep184
programme.desc: The beauty of folklore is all around us in Taiwan, but we often overlook it and fail to appreciate and feel it. The aim of this program is to promote the beauty of Taiwanese folklore and bring folklore to life. This program showcases folk culture regardless of race or religion, and presents travel information in a fun way, combining easy-to-understand folk culture knowledge with the mission of passing on folk culture. The audience can learn more about folk cultural products such as handicrafts, antiques, temple folklore, as well as short stories about the gods, and information about local tourism. It is an educational and entertaining way to travel and learn about folklore.

programme.title: Have A Nice Dream (M) Ep101
programme.desc: Five young professionals with different life skills, team up for two days and one night trip, leading the audiance to explore the good life of nature and the beauty of the land of Taiwan.

programme.title: Way to Health(M) Ep241242
programme.desc: This show invites top medical professionals from different fields to answer questions from the audience. Approved by the medical world, this show is an influential, as well as reliable place to understand more about ones health.

programme.title: Mr.Player (M) Ep476
programme.desc: Depending on the locations of the missions, Jacky Wu, the leader of the home team, invites various celebrities to take on challenges and bring you excitement every week.

programme.title: Home Sweet Home(M) Ep12
programme.desc: Every one of them showed up in this house with some sort of lacking until they've met Mommy Hsiao-Li. Although they are not biologicap related, they Stay with each other like a real family.

programme.title: Still Human
programme.desc: Evelyn, a Filipino domestic helper, moves to Hong Kong to work for Cheong Wing, a divorcee paralyzed in a construction accident. Becoming unlikely friends, the two discover shared humanity that helps them face lifes mounting hardships.

programme.title: Eternal Wave
programme.desc: Lin Xiang is a spy trying to rebuild an underground informant network in Shanghai after the Japanese Occupation. He meets a simple but righteous girl who acts as his wife in the secret mission. When Lin is captured after his identity was revealed, his wife comes to save him but can they escape from the foes?

programme.title: American Girl
programme.desc: 13 year-old Fen is uprooted from LA and moves to Taipei in early 2003, when her mother is diagnosed with breast cancer. She struggles to adjust to her new life with a new school and long-separated father, and drifts away from her mother. When her younger sister is misdiagnosed with SARS, they finally open up to each other during quarantine.

programme.title: Bodies at Rest
programme.desc: When three armed criminals barge into a morgue, a forensic doctor and his student must fight with their lives to stop the criminals from obtaining a bullet from inside a corpse that is a key piece of evidence in a deadly crime.

programme.title: The Italian Recipe
programme.desc: Famous pop idol Peng travels to Rome for a reality show and encounters an ordinary girl, Mang, who dreams of becoming a great chef after migrating to Italy. Peng and Mang have nothing in common but spend a magical night in Rome together. Their lives begin to change as the two start to fall in love.

programme.title: Raging Fire
programme.desc: As the police sets to arrest a drug lord, a team of masked thugs steals the drugs and murders the cops. Inspector Bong is devastated to see the aftermath of the carnage and soon discovers that the killers are led by Ngo, a former fellow cop who was forced into a life of crime by him. As the two men meet again, it is time to settle the score

programme.title: May Who?
programme.desc: The story is about a super standard girl in school, May Who, is on a quest to win the love of a school senior heart-throbber, Fame, with her new-found friend, Pong. The only secret is that she can discharge electricity when she gets excited

programme.title: A Cool Fish
programme.desc: In this dark-comedy, cop-turned-security guard Ma faces the ultimate challenge when his boss mysteriously disappears and his paralyzed sister makes a morbid deal with the armed bandits who abduct her.

programme.title: Touch of the Light
programme.desc: A blind but talented pianist Siang encounters an unrecognized but skilful dancer Chieh. Chieh is attracted to the courageous Siang while Siang is fascinated by the adventurous Chieh. Their friendship grows as Siang and Chieh pursue their dreams together. Sandrine Pinna was awarded Best Actress for her role as Chieh in the 2012 Taipei Film Festival.

programme.title: Iron Kung Fu Fist
programme.desc: Liang Kun is a skilled martial arts master who left the martial arts world to protect his lover. However, his disappearance leads to her tragic death and as Liang Kun finds a way to survive in the martial arts world, he fights back to avenge his lovers death with the help of a beggar gang leader.

programme.title: The Knight of Shadows: Between Yin and Yang
programme.desc: Pu Song Ling, a legendary demon hunter, is asked to investigate a case involving missing teenage village girls with disciple, Constable Yan Fei. The duo leads a group of little monsters to help with the investigation, and in their search for the truth, they accidentally discover a mysterious love between a knight and a female ghost.

programme.title: Fall in Love at First Kiss
programme.desc: In this romantic love story starring Taiwanese actors Darren Wang and Jelly Lin, an ordinary girl develops a stubborn crush on the school genius after an unexpected kiss. But with the genius adored by everyone in the school, can their relationship blossom and develop?

programme.title: High Risk
programme.desc: After failing to save his wife, Kit resigned as a cop and becomes the bodyguard and stunt double for a cowardly action film star, Frankie. When attending a jewel exhibition, they run into a band of robbers. Kit identifies the murderer of his wife amongst them and chases after him. Will Frankie regain his courage to help Kit?

programme.title: Call Me Agent
programme.desc: Miu Ling dreams of becoming a secret agent. Even though it seems impossible, she still harbours such a dream and hopes that it will soon come true. One day, Miu Ling rescues an injured secret agent who promises to make her his apprentice. From then on, her life is turned upside down and she goes onto a roller-coaster of madcap adventures.

programme.title: The Calling of a Bus Driver
programme.desc: A girl named Suki fulfills her dream of being a bus driver after breaking up with her boyfriend, who has an affair with her good friend. When Suki is invited to attend her ex-boyfriends wedding, she is presented with a chance for revenge will she take it and turn her life around?

programme.title: Wusong VS Ximenqing
programme.desc: Wu Song finds out about his sister-in-laws affair with a rich man, Ximen Qing. Qing sets Song up and have him exiled for a year, during which his hapless brother is murdered and cremated. When Song finally returns home, he takes the case to court but the judge brushes it aside and closes it abruptly. Can Song finally avenge his brothers death?

programme.title: Love Revolution
programme.desc: Ai Yoshida will do anything for love, including traveling to Thailand with her boyfriend from Japan to run dope. When her boyfriend is kidnapped by the local gangster after a brawl at a bar, Ai sets out on a rescue mission that sends her on an action-packed roller-coaster ride where she meets a professional assassin who breaks out of jail for love.

programme.title: Justice, My Foot!
programme.desc: Chow stars as Sung, a lawyer who uses any means necessary to help his wealthy clients escape the law. Sung retires to the countryside when urged by his wife, but when Mrs Sung encounters a woman whose husband's death has been covered up by corrupted officials, Sung returns to the court for justice to be served.

programme.title: Once Upon a Time in Hong Kong
programme.desc: This is a story of ICAC investigators fighting against rampant corruption in early 1970s Hong Kong. A police sergeant teams up with a triad boss to make billions of dollars in bribes. As a lawyer joins his friend in ICAC to investigate their collusion and fight against corruption, the battle between the righteous and the wicked has just begun.

programme.title: My Blue Summer
programme.desc: Zhi has been secretly in love with Nan since she met him once as a child. After graduating high school, Zhi realizes that she and Nan are in the same university, where they get to know each other by chance and become close friends. However, Zhi is still too shy to express her love for Nan. Will this long-term crush finally turn into true love?

programme.title: Model Family
programme.desc: A single-parent family (Yu Xiang and Tong Tong) move into a new neighbourhood where everyones life seems perfect. However, while things may look rosy on the outside, dark secrets and horror raid each family from the inside, and nothing really are as they seem.

programme.title: The Monkey is Back
programme.desc: The savior of the people, Stone Monkey, has given hope to a desperate little girl which he promises to realize. Years later, Stone Monkey is defeated in a battle with the three-eyed God of War, causing him to lose his power and falls into the mortal world. Can he fulfill his promise to the girl and stop the God of Wood from destroying earth?

programme.title: Chinese Odyssey 2002
programme.desc: Set in Ming Dynasty, young Emperor Zheng De escapes from the palace with his sister who disguised as a man. They run into a notorious wanderer who runs a restaurant with his boyish sister in Jiang Nan. The two pairs of siblings from vastly different social classes descend into an inescapable swirl of gender confusion, slapstick antics and love.

programme.title: HK Lan Kwai Fong
programme.desc: Lee is the Production head of an advertising firm who tries to improve her teams performance by competing with Creative head Chan in the day and clubbing at Lan Kwai Fong for ideas at night. Lee runs into her ex-boyfriend before a big commercial shoot and drowns her sorrows drinking at Lan Kwai Fong, but finally picks herself up with Chans help.

programme.title: Quan Dao: The Journey of a Boxer
programme.desc: Ah Niu learns boxing from Uncle Xing, the boss of a boxing studio, since young and uses his skills to help the weak fight villains. When Xings son attempts drug trafficking to save his fathers studio but fails and is brutally beaten up, Ah Niu accepts a death combat challenge so as to help him take revenge.

programme.title: Beyond the Dream
programme.desc: Primary school teacher Lok is a recovering schizophrenic who falls in love with a young girl he first met. As he struggles to reveal his illness, Lok has a relapse and becomes delusional. Little does he know she is a mental health counsellor who has a hidden agenda. The pair develops a relationship that is beyond their wildest dreams.

programme.title: Vanguard
programme.desc: A businessman Qin Guo Li is being kidnapped in London and his daughter is also in danger. The international security team, Vanguard, is hired to rescue them. Tang Huan Ting, the founder, gathers an elite team to track them down across countries, from London to Africa and Dubai. In the process, they also discover another dangerous conspiracy.

programme.title: The Silent War
programme.desc: After the Chinese Civil War, 701 Bureau continues to monitor the coded transmissions between rebel forces. When radio frequencies used by the opponent disappear suddenly, Agent Zhang asks Ho, a blind piano tuner with exceptional hearing, to help find the transmission signals. Can Ho find the missing signals and foil a possible assassination plot?

programme.title: Wu Xia
programme.desc: Martial artist Liu hides his identity and lives in a remote village with his wife Ah Yu and their two sons, but somehow gets embroiled in a bizarre murder case. Constable Xu is a kung fu fanatic, whose curiosity forces Liu into a death duel with the Sect Leader of the 72 Demons, and puts Lius family and homeland in a great danger...

programme.title: Naked Soldier
programme.desc: When Interpol agent Long busted a billion-dollar drug deal 15 years ago, the cartel took revenge and killed his family. The cartel boss, Madame Rose, even kidnaps and raises Longs daughter, Phoenix, to become a skilled assassin. Only when Phoenix is about to kill Long did she discover the startling fact about her true identity

programme.title: Red Line
programme.desc: A former professional car racer, Le falls into despair after causing his brother's death in a car race, until he meets female doctor Hui and becomes an ambulance driver who vows to save lives with speed. Meanwhile, the truth about his brothers accident emerges with the investigation of Le's three good friends...

programme.title: Mr & Mrs Incredible
programme.desc: Middle-aged and retired superhero couple, Huan (Gazer Man) and Red (Aroma Woman), settles into a contented life in a remote village. They find it hard to contain their powers though, and are bored by the uneventful life. When they hear a world martial arts contest is to be held in their village, both are itching to make their long-awaited comeback!

programme.title: The Dream Of The Red Chamber
programme.desc: Adapted from the great Chinese classic novel of the same name, the son of renowned Jia family, Bao Yu, is deeply in love with his cousin, Dai Yu. However, his mother disapproves of their relationship and plots to arrange Bao Yu to marry another rich girl, resulting in a tragic ending for the perfect couple.

programme.title: King Gambler
programme.desc: This film was actually a lively forerunner to the gambling film craze, which eventually swept Asian cinema. Here, it's cardsharp versus cardsharp with a lot more kung-fu action, in a battle of wits and fists to become the king of the casino. The double stings and triple crosses raise in complexity and imagination until what started as an unusual box office risk became a top ten hit of 1976.

programme.title: The Empress Dowager
programme.desc: Award-winning drama featuring a passionate performance by Lisa Lu, enhanced by sumptuous costumes and sets, produces a powerful, fascinating story. In five thousand years of Chinese history, there was never a more fascinating woman than the dragon lady of the Ching Dynasty, also the Empress Dowager, who was the power behind the throne for the last half of the 19th century. The vast tapestry of palace intrigues is vividly brought to the screen.

programme.title: The Gambling Syndicate
programme.desc: A young provincial detective seeks to take down a local gambling syndicate with the help of two convicts.

programme.title: The Kingdom And The Beauty
programme.desc: Emperor Cheng Te meets country maiden Li Feng on a visit to Southern China. It was love at first sight and the Emperor leaves with a promise that Li Feng would be his empress. When he sends for Li one year later, she was too ill to withstand the arduous journey and arrives just in time to die in the arms of her beloved...

programme.title: The Invincible Fist
programme.desc: A dedicated chief constable nicknamed The Invincible Fist is chasing after a band of bandits near a village one day and encounters an innocent blind girl. He quickly falls in love with her, but finds out she is the daughter of a vicious bandit. Will he kill the father of his lover?

programme.title: The Warlord
programme.desc: A bandit became a warlord in northern China by helping Russia fight against Japan. Due to his ignorance and silly behaviour, he is seen as a joke to everyone. The warlord is finally killed by the daughter of a troupe master whom he had killed for no reason, bringing a befitting end to a traitor.

programme.title: Martial Arts Of Shaolin
programme.desc: Zhi Ming, who trains at the Northern Shaolin Temple, teams up with Si Ma Yan, who trains at the Southern Shaolin Temple, to avenge both their fathers death by assassinating a corrupt magistrate, leading to a series of fierce battles!

programme.title: Two Con Men
programme.desc: Two Con Men is a wonderfully twisted, pseudo-romantic comedy in the vein of "Robin Hood" meets "The Sting". Starring Liang Tien as Clever Chan and Chang Ying (who's done over 400 films) as Tricky Ching, it's the age-old competition between a rookie con artist versus the ultimate, experienced flimflam man. It's a game Chen cannot afford to lose, because people's lives - including his own, hang in the balance of good versus evil.

programme.title: The Black Butterfly
programme.desc: Kwan leads a double life as a waitress and as an infamous outlaw skilled in martial arts, The Black Butterfly. When she steals a cache of gold from the Five Devils Rock bandits, she soon has the bandits, and the government, on her tail.

programme.title: Intimate Confessions Of A Chinese Courtesan
programme.desc: Young Ai Nu is abducted and sold to the popular Four Seasons brothel run by the powerful and ruthless Madam Chun Yi. Ai Nu gets locked up in a dungeon due to her fiery attitude. Soon, a murder occurs within the brothel and a policeman must race against time to prevent a vicious revenge plot from reaching its blood-spattered conclusion.

programme.title: That Fiery Girl
programme.desc: The bandits of Hulu Valley slay the chief of the Mei Clan while searching for a treasure map. In retaliation, Chun from the Mei Clan infiltrates the bandit's fortress to map a way in for the authorities, but ends up falling in love with the bandit leader's daughter, Pearl. While Chuns plot is uncovered, he receives unexpected help from Pearl.

programme.title: The Avenging Eagle
programme.desc: Qi Ming Xing, an assassin of the Iron Boat Clan, decides to quit the clan. When hunted by the clan, he is saved by Swordsman Zhuo Yi Fan. Zhuo accidentally discovers that Qi is the killer of his wife, but he forgives Qi after knowing Qis guilt over her death. The two finally team up to destroy the evil clan.

programme.title: The Monkey Goes West
programme.desc: The story follows Monk Tang San Zangs journey to the West in search of the Buddhist Sutra. On the way, he encounters and takes as disciples, Monkey, Pigsy and Sha Wu Jing.

programme.title: Shaolin Intruders
programme.desc: On a routine courier mission, the prestigious Chief was murdered by four mysterious monks. When all evidence pointed to Ching Hua, his friend Lei decides to clear his name by barging in the Shaolin Temple thrice. When Lei thought justice was served for the culprits, he soon realizes the table had turned and the monks stroke again. What follows is a series of intense pursuit for the ultimate villain!

programme.title: Lover'S Rock
programme.desc: Pan Lei, winner the China Literary Award for three consecutive years, wrote and directed this film about the lives and loves of a fishing village. It starred the glorious Cheng Pei-pei in her first film as a woman (she had debuted in a mans role), and her much-lauded performance won her the prestigious Golden Accolade Award from the International Association Of Independent Producers a first for any Asian woman.

programme.title: Angel With The Iron Fists
programme.desc: Lo Wei directs and stars as the chief detective in this gripping thriller; playing alongside Lily Ho, who excels in the role of an undercover avenger that can fight as well as she flirts! Caught between the crime bosses known as Baldhead and Black Widow, she only has four choices: punch, kick, shoot or bombard with explosives!

programme.title: Princess Iron Fan
programme.desc: As Monkey and his gang make their way to the West through Fire Mountain, they ran into the evil Princess Iron Fan, Madam White Bone and her sexy sister, and have to fight their way through.

programme.title: Lady With A Sword
programme.desc: Swordswoman Feng tries to find a group of villains responsible for her eldest sister's death, but is shocked to discover that her fianc, Jin, is one of them. At the same time, Jin's mother and the two other killers are planning to kill Feng. Can Feng fight back and take her revenge?

programme.title: Dawn Will Come
programme.desc: Liang Cai drugged the beautiful Qiu Rong and raped her, but promised to marry her after getting his parents consent. Since then, there is no news of his proposal and Qiu Rong confronts Liang Cai when she finds herself pregnant. This is when she discovers that he has already married a rich noble girl and even plans to kill her

programme.title: Clan Feuds
programme.desc: Like legendary director Chu Yuan did so often and so successfully, Chang Peng Yi adapted this film from a story by Ku Lung. Following the footsteps of the equally legendary Chang Cheh, Chang also casted the majestic Ti Lung, along with "Venoms Lo Meng and Sun Chien, for a spectacular showcase of mystical Martial Arts Worlds intrigue and consummate Kung Fu.

programme.title: Hex
programme.desc: This supernatural mystery tells the story of a sickly wife and her maid conspiring to kill her beastly husband, leading to a string of events with spooky twists and turns.

programme.title: To Kill A Jaguar
programme.desc: Set in 1920s Shanghai, a village girl journeys to the big city in search of her father and meets her childhood friend Jaguar, who works for the mob boss Kam. In a world controlled by the mobs, it is a test of survival for all as Jaguar allies himself with ace gunman Ko Tang, to take over Kams empire.

programme.title: Love Without End
programme.desc: Lin Dai stars in this romantic classic as a nightclub singer who falls for a young architect. When he suffers grave financial difficulty, she does the unthinkable to help him.

programme.title: The Spiritual Boxer
programme.desc: One of the first kung fu comedies, this is a story about a con artist who uses kung fu to swindle villagers for money by pretending to be possessed by spirits. When they are threatened by bandits, he must use the same skills for good.

programme.title: The Long Chase
programme.desc: Governor Yan is killed and his guard Fan identifies Kou as the assassin by his signature weapon, a dart. Kou is listed as a wanted man when he enters the city, but managed to escape arrest with the help of the innkeepers daughter. At the same time, Fan is attacked by a bandit who pretends to be Kou. What are the secret plots behind these attacks?

programme.title: The Pearl Phoenix
programme.desc: In Huangmei Opera tradition, this movie tells the love story of Wen, who sells himself as a slave to a rich family, and Huo, the familys young daughter. The lovers are kept apart by Huos stepmother and Huo escapes by dressing up as a man. Wen is framed and put into jail so Huo has to go back and rescue her lover!

programme.title: Heaven And Hell
programme.desc: When an angel, Ling, decides to help his two friends who have fallen in love to escape from Heaven, he is sent to live as a human on earth as his punishment. Reincarnated as a cab driver, he sacrifices his own life to save another ill-fated couple and lands in hell, where he has to face off against the ghosts and demons to fight his way out!

programme.title: My Name Ain'T Suzie
programme.desc: Young Mei Li works as a bar girl in Wanchai to make a living. When she meets Jimmy in the bar, she thinks he is her true love and falls crazily in love with him. When Jimmy has to leave, Mei Li is devastated. It is not until she encounters the triad boss Ying that she finally found someone to count on.

programme.title: The Black Enforcer
programme.desc: Lung the Black Enforcer is ordered to escort a murderer Fei to prison. While taking shelter in Lungs house from the snowstorm, Fei is rescued by his gang and Fei kills Lungs mother and sister before escaping. Lung is imprisoned for the failed task and after being released, he vows to avenge his family by killing Fei.

programme.title: Emperor Chien Lung
programme.desc: Emperor Chien Lung goes incognito to mix with his people and understand their needs. He encounters many strange things along the way, including being arrested and nearly beheaded. Who will save him?

programme.title: Heroes Of The East
programme.desc: A Chinese man marries a Japanese woman through an arranged marriage and manages to insult all of her Japanese martial arts family by issuing a challenge to her that is misinterpreted by the others. He must then prove how good Chinese Kung Fu really is through a series of duels with the seven Japanese martial artists who come to meet the challenge!

programme.title: Forever And Ever
programme.desc: Ivy Ling Po plays a young scholar who is manipulated into marrying a nobleman's reluctant daughter. After marrying, he soon discovers the reason for her hesitation. She is stricken with a contagious disease. But, with the power of true love, their romance prevails.

programme.title: Men From The Monastery
programme.desc: At the end of the Ming Dynasty, Wu San Gui betrays his people to the Qing officials and recruits fighters from all backgrounds. Members from Wudan and Ermei are the first to yield and collude with local bullies. When they start attacking the Shaolin Monastery, its most famous disciples have to band together and fight against the enemies.

programme.title: We Love Millionaires
programme.desc: In this romantic comedy, three beautiful Hong Kong salesgirls travel to Osaka in Japan to pursue their dreams of marrying a rich man. They masquerade as high society debutantes and make their way to a posh resort to meet and woo millionaires (or fake ones!).

programme.title: Malawi Wildlife Rescue 1 Ep2

programme.title: New Kids in the Wild 1 Ep3

programme.desc: Prelims - On October 21, the UFC returns to Abu Dhabi, where two of the top fighters in the world, pound for pound, will meet again as Islam Makhachev defends his lightweight title against featherweight champion Alexander Volkanovski in the main event of UFC 294 at Etihad Arena.
